Catalyst::Model::XMLRPC version 0.04
=======================================

Catalyst model that provide a simple way to communicate with remote processes
using XML-RPC.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Perl modules:

  Catalyst
  Catalyst::Devel
  NEXT
  RPC::XML
  Test::More

